{"title":"java时间格式化任意格式","date":"2019-02-28T01:33:22.000Z","link":"post/314","categories":["Java"],"updated":"2019-04-26T15:04:57.359Z","content":"<figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">/**</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">\t * 将String型格式化,比如想要将2011-11-11格式化成2011年11月11日,就StringPattern(\"2011-11-11\",</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">\t * \"yyyy-MM-dd\",\"yyyy年MM月dd日\").</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">\t * </span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">\t * <span class=\"doctag\">@param</span> date</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">\t *            String 想要格式化的日期</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">\t * <span class=\"doctag\">@param</span> oldPattern</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">\t *            String 想要格式化的日期的现有格式</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">\t * <span class=\"doctag\">@param</span> newPattern</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">\t *            String 想要格式化成什么格式</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">\t * <span class=\"doctag\">@return</span> String</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">\t */</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span> String <span class=\"title\">StringPattern</span><span class=\"params\">(String date, String oldPattern, String newPattern)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (date == <span class=\"keyword\">null</span> || oldPattern == <span class=\"keyword\">null</span> || newPattern == <span class=\"keyword\">null</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"string\">\"\"</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tSimpleDateFormat sdf1 = <span class=\"keyword\">new</span> SimpleDateFormat(oldPattern); <span class=\"comment\">// 实例化模板对象</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tSimpleDateFormat sdf2 = <span class=\"keyword\">new</span> SimpleDateFormat(newPattern); <span class=\"comment\">// 实例化模板对象</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tDate d = <span class=\"keyword\">null</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"keyword\">try</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\td = sdf1.parse(date); <span class=\"comment\">// 将给定的字符串中的日期提取出来</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t&#125; <span class=\"keyword\">catch</span> (Exception e) &#123; <span class=\"comment\">// 如果提供的字符串格式有错误，则进行异常处理</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\te.printStackTrace(); <span class=\"comment\">// 打印异常信息</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"keyword\">return</span> sdf2.format(d);</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>","prev":{"title":"String.format详解","link":"post/316"},"next":{"title":"mybatis配置log4j控制台打印SQL语句","link":"post/313"},"plink":"https://1056438464.github.io/post/314/"}